《'''在德丁斯顿湖溜冰的罗伯特·沃克牧师'''》（'''''The Reverend Robert Walker Skating on Duddingston Loch'''''），常稱《'''滑冰的牧師'''》（'''''The Skating Minister'''''）是[[亨利·雷伯恩|亨利·雷伯恩]]爵士繪製於1790年代的一幅油畫作品，現藏於英國[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]][[蘇格蘭國家畫廊|蘇格蘭國家畫廊]]。實際上在1949年之前這幅畫都沒什麼名氣，之後卻成為了雷伯恩最著名的的畫作之一。它繪製於[[蘇格蘭啟蒙|蘇格蘭啟蒙]]時代，也被當做是[[蘇格蘭文化|蘇格蘭文化]]的象征。有人懷疑這幅畫其實是法國畫家Henri-Pierre Danloux的作品，但此說沒有得到學界的一致認可。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://news.scotsman.com/news/Doubts-over-Skating-Minister-cut.2614249.jp| title = Doubts over Skating Minister cut no ice with art experts| author = Blackley, Michael| date = 2005-03-30| accessdate = 2010-05-28| newspaper = The Scotsman| archive-date = 2011-08-07| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110807170503/http://news.scotsman.com/news/Doubts-over-Skating-Minister-cut.2614249.jp| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.heraldscotland.com/sport/spl/aberdeen/the-skating-minister-enduring-masterpiece-by-the-great-scottish-artist-henry-raeburn-or-just-a-rather-nice-painting-by-an-obscure-frenchman-as-the-controversy-rages-on-over-the-authorship-of-a-national-icon-alan-taylor-attempts-to-untangle-the-myster-1.46642| title = The Skating Minister: enduring masterpiece by the great Scottish artist Henry Raeburn, or just a rather nice painting by an obscure Frenchman?| author = Taylor, Alan| date = 2005-08-07| accessdate = 2010-05-28| newspaper = The Herald, Scotland| archive-date = 2014-12-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141206104006/http://www.heraldscotland.com/sport/spl/aberdeen/the-skating-minister-enduring-masterpiece-by-the-great-scottish-artist-henry-raeburn-or-just-a-rather-nice-painting-by-an-obscure-frenchman-as-the-controversy-rages-on-over-the-authorship-of-a-national-icon-alan-taylor-attempts-to-untangle-the-myster-1.46642| dead-url = no}}</ref>

畫中人物是[[蘇格蘭長老會|蘇格蘭長老會]]牧師[[羅伯特·沃克_(牧師)|羅伯特·沃克]]，他父親即是該教會成員，1770年15歲時羅伯特·沃克成為愛丁堡長老（Presbytery of Edinburgh），後來加入了[[愛丁堡滑冰俱樂部|愛丁堡滑冰俱樂部]]，這是世界上最早成立的花樣滑冰俱樂部。 <ref name=Hines2011>{{cite book|first=James R. |last=Hines |title=Historical Dictionary of Figure Skating |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=LSEkqy6BS44C&pg=PA150 |date=2011-04-22 |publisher=Scarecrow Press |isbn=978-0-8108-7085-7 |page=150}}</ref>

